data.description: Check out this cozy slice of paradise in Smithdale, Mississippi. This roomy 2,560 sq ft 2011 double-wide mobile home is located in West Lincoln School district and features 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. This Lincoln County home is situated on 7.65+/- acres. Inside, you're greeted by a welcoming fireplace that adds some down-home warmth to the spacious living areas, creating the perfect spot for get-togethers. The large kitchen and 4 bedrooms offer plenty of space to unwind, and the 3 bathrooms keep things convenient for everyone. Step outside, and you've got acres of land to roam, ideal for all sorts of outdoor fun, plus there's a pond that just adds to the laid-back Southern charm. The storage shed and a 2-car carport are perfect for extra storage space. This property effortlessly blends that good ol' country feel with the modern comforts you need. Don't let this chance pass you by! Schedule a visit today and make this your very own!
